So many martial artists are locked here.

21
00:02:01,720 --> 00:02:02,710
How can you save them?

22
00:02:07,110 --> 00:02:08,850
Simple. Get them all out.

23
00:02:11,200 --> 00:02:12,120
Young lady,

24
00:02:12,540 --> 00:02:14,720
the situation is complicated
and dangerous.

25
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:15,690
There isn’t much you can do

26
00:02:15,690 --> 00:02:16,980
on your own.

27
00:02:21,530 --> 00:02:22,330
Well,

28
00:02:22,540 --> 00:02:24,140
I can tell you about the layout

29
00:02:24,140 --> 00:02:25,230
and the posts.

30
00:02:35,050 --> 00:02:36,760
How did you know all that?

31
00:02:38,330 --> 00:02:40,240
You think I’d wait to rot in here?

32
00:02:40,740 --> 00:02:41,920
This lock couldn’t stop me.

33
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:43,300
I’ve gone out more than once.

34
00:02:45,410 --> 00:02:47,320
If so,

35
00:02:47,770 --> 00:02:49,510
why didn’t you help others?

36
00:02:53,430 --> 00:02:54,690
Have you forgotten

37
00:02:55,050 --> 00:02:57,210
I’m poisoned?

38
00:02:57,750 --> 00:02:58,400
I mean,

39
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:00,580
how could I rescue others?

40
00:03:03,900 --> 00:03:07,050
Look, we’re in a two-story

41
00:03:07,180 --> 00:03:08,330
heavily guarded dungeon.

42
00:03:12,270 --> 00:03:12,910
If you

43
00:03:13,660 --> 00:03:14,470
can make it here,

44
00:03:15,310 --> 00:03:16,260
you’ll be able to get out.

45
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:18,120
Got it?

46
00:03:20,430 --> 00:03:22,600
Weed Spirit! Weed Spirit!

47
00:04:00,490 --> 00:04:01,630
Weed Spirit!

48
00:04:03,430 --> 00:04:04,490
How did you get in?

49
00:04:05,070 --> 00:04:05,930
Am I good?

50
00:04:07,190 --> 00:04:08,010
Open it!

51
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:25,060
The routes you drew are too messy.

52
00:04:25,060 --> 00:04:26,630
I can’t see them clearly.

53
00:04:45,310 --> 00:04:46,000
Miss,

54
00:04:46,850 --> 00:04:48,000
can you read a map or not?

55
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:51,400
It’s about time.

56
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:52,260
Hurry up.

57
00:04:53,820 --> 00:04:54,430
Be quiet!

58
00:05:00,980 --> 00:05:02,450
This dungeon is filled

59
00:05:02,450 --> 00:05:04,450
with prisoners from top to bottom.

60
00:05:09,780 --> 00:05:11,780
Guards change shifts every two hours

61
00:05:11,780 --> 00:05:12,920
when the clapper sounds.

62
00:05:19,640 --> 00:05:20,450
I see.

63
00:05:21,340 --> 00:05:22,120
By the way,

64
00:05:24,110 --> 00:05:25,140
if you run into

65
00:05:25,290 --> 00:05:27,000
someone in red,

66
00:05:27,210 --> 00:05:28,140
just leave immediately.

67
00:05:28,140 --> 00:05:28,910
Do not hesitate.

68
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,220
Those old fogies

69
00:05:31,220 --> 00:05:33,100
have been to hell and back.

70
00:05:33,270 --> 00:05:34,930
They’ll sure get themselves out.

71
00:05:34,930 --> 00:05:36,530
Stay out of trouble.

72
00:05:39,020 --> 00:05:39,960
Just go home

73
00:05:39,960 --> 00:05:41,170
and tell your seniors

74
00:05:41,170 --> 00:05:42,340
to ask the Huo’s for your people.

75
00:05:44,010 --> 00:05:44,750
Don’t worry.

76
00:05:45,190 --> 00:05:46,370
At this point,

77
00:05:46,530 --> 00:05:48,820
Huo Liantao wouldn’t say no
to your leader.

78
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:50,960
He’ll certainly

79
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:52,500
release Chenfei.

80
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:54,790
Then what?

81
00:05:55,340 --> 00:05:56,370
What about you?

82
00:06:00,270 --> 00:06:01,880
Last night, the stars showed

83
00:06:02,450 --> 00:06:05,140
chaos would soon rise.

84
00:06:08,390 --> 00:06:09,920
Just pretend you don’t know anything.

85
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:11,340
Find the ones you’re looking for

86
00:06:11,550 --> 00:06:12,570
and leave.

87
00:06:28,710 --> 00:06:30,100
Why are you staring at me?

88
00:06:33,220 --> 00:06:35,040
I have principles.

89
00:06:35,630 --> 00:06:36,780
I’d never ask a girl

90
00:06:36,780 --> 00:06:37,970
to take any risks.

91
00:06:39,200 --> 00:06:40,640
I enjoy staying here.

92
00:06:41,710 --> 00:06:43,510
The three of us are having fun.

93
00:06:43,700 --> 00:06:45,510
I can stay for two more months
without feeling lonely.

94
00:06:48,380 --> 00:06:49,820
Why is there the three of you?

95
00:06:51,990 --> 00:06:52,890
The blazing sun,

96
00:06:53,100 --> 00:06:54,220
the clear sky,

97
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:55,450
and me.

98
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:01,030
Are you sure it’s not
stone, sand and you?

99
00:07:04,630 --> 00:07:06,360
You’re too sick

100
00:07:06,550 --> 00:07:07,340
to be cured

101
00:07:08,030 --> 00:07:08,960
I guess.

102
00:07:09,830 --> 00:07:10,730
Hey.

103
00:07:20,260 --> 00:07:21,360
Once

104
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,920
I’m out

105
00:07:23,010 --> 00:07:24,490
and you aren’t home yet,

106
00:07:24,730 --> 00:07:25,790
I’ll join you.

107
00:07:30,260 --> 00:07:32,330
There’s something important
that you should have.

108
00:07:36,970 --> 00:07:37,880
Last time,

109
00:07:38,150 --> 00:07:39,370
although I was ordered

110
00:07:39,690 --> 00:07:41,120
to break into your place,

111
00:07:41,550 --> 00:07:43,770
your parents were
separated because of me.

112
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:49,510
And your blade was broken, too.

113
00:07:51,960 --> 00:07:53,160
I’m surprised you still remember that.

114
00:07:55,730 --> 00:07:58,300
It’s always been on my mind

115
00:07:58,620 --> 00:08:00,140
and I’m planning to make you a new one.

116
00:08:02,590 --> 00:08:03,750
But

117
00:08:04,540 --> 00:08:05,990
the materials are still lacking.

118
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:07,130
So

119
00:08:08,130 --> 00:08:09,630
I can only give you
a wooden one for now.

120
00:08:15,460 --> 00:08:17,830
The real one has to wait.

121
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:24,320
Are you...

122
00:08:35,730 --> 00:08:36,930
Are you not leaving with me?

123
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:40,370
The two of us will make a bigger target.

124
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:42,020
The guards have already been alerted

125
00:08:42,020 --> 00:08:44,020
when you came in.

126
00:08:44,350 --> 00:08:46,120
They’re after you as we speak.

127
00:08:49,140 --> 00:08:50,010
Relax.

128
00:08:50,290 --> 00:08:51,100
I’m blessed.

129
00:08:51,340 --> 00:08:51,940
You should

130
00:08:51,940 --> 00:08:53,570
leave without me.

131
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:56,960
At least, you can be the messenger.

132
00:09:03,370 --> 00:09:04,460
You can’t die

133
00:09:04,460 --> 00:09:05,740
before paying off your debts.

134
00:09:07,870 --> 00:09:08,550
I know.

135
00:09:24,170 --> 00:09:26,260
I wasn’t taught to be a deserter.

136
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:28,800
How could I go back

137
00:09:28,950 --> 00:09:30,800
without finding them?

138
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:32,890
Besides...

139
00:09:36,790 --> 00:09:38,630
I didn’t expect to see her here.

140
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:41,230
That girl is

141
00:09:41,670 --> 00:09:43,230
a real troublemaker.

142
00:09:45,610 --> 00:09:47,260
Is she out yet?

143
00:09:59,800 --> 00:10:00,420
Let’s go.

144
00:10:00,420 --> 00:10:01,860
OK. Coming.

145
00:10:02,300 --> 00:10:04,830
Guards change shifts every two hours

146
00:10:04,830 --> 00:10:05,780
when the clapper sounds.

147
00:10:06,650 --> 00:10:07,940
At that time,

148
00:10:07,940 --> 00:10:10,350
guards of the first shift
will pass by the pavilion and leave.

149
00:10:13,510 --> 00:10:14,540
Is there anything wrong?

150
00:10:14,540 --> 00:10:15,170
No.

151
00:10:15,300 --> 00:10:16,160
Their replacements

152
00:10:16,160 --> 00:10:18,230
will patrol around briefly.

153
00:10:19,450 --> 00:10:21,120
At that moment,

154
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:23,150
the post will be left empty.

155
00:10:23,740 --> 00:10:24,840
You can go there.

156
00:10:45,060 --> 00:10:46,550
If they see me,

157
00:10:48,330 --> 00:10:50,210
I’ll fight my way out.

158
00:11:13,780 --> 00:11:14,590
Let’s go.

159
00:11:18,980 --> 00:11:20,010
Come on.

160
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:24,240
Coming.

161
00:11:31,660 --> 00:11:33,380
There might be antidotes here.

162
00:11:41,810 --> 00:11:43,410
Those bastards

163
00:11:43,620 --> 00:11:44,620
are treating themselves so well

164
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:46,480
while feeding others poison.

165
00:11:48,500 --> 00:11:49,960
Take that way to search.

166
00:11:50,470 --> 00:11:51,300
Go.

167
00:11:52,810 --> 00:11:53,810
Go over there.

168
00:11:58,520 --> 00:11:59,000
Let’s go.

169
00:12:07,170 --> 00:12:08,450
That’s a strong force.

170
00:12:17,390 --> 00:12:18,850
He looks

171
00:12:18,850 --> 00:12:20,740
weaker than Father.

172
00:12:21,680 --> 00:12:22,740
Thank you.

173
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:26,580
Sir...

174
00:12:27,330 --> 00:12:27,920
are you...

175
00:12:29,210 --> 00:12:30,260
are you alright?

176
00:12:31,090 --> 00:12:32,840
Who are you?

177
00:12:34,100 --> 00:12:35,860
What are you doing here?

178
00:12:36,880 --> 00:12:38,360
You’re the one

179
00:12:38,610 --> 00:12:40,360
they’re looking for, aren’t you?

180
00:12:43,010 --> 00:12:45,110
One of my cousins

181
00:12:45,510 --> 00:12:46,990
were caught

182
00:12:46,990 --> 00:12:48,250
on an outing.

183
00:12:48,250 --> 00:12:49,220
I’m here to look for him.

184
00:12:50,140 --> 00:12:51,220
Sorry for disturbing you.

185
00:12:52,070 --> 00:12:53,750
Who taught you your skills?

186
00:12:58,390 --> 00:13:00,620
They were created by my ancestors.

187
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:05,860
My parents and I

188
00:13:06,730 --> 00:13:08,070
don’t take them too seriously.

189
00:13:08,070 --> 00:13:09,130
I only practice them for health.

190
00:13:12,690 --> 00:13:14,150
And our family is small

191
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:17,640
even with two more cousins,

192
00:13:17,640 --> 00:13:19,410
unlike those prestigious sects.

193
00:13:31,450 --> 00:13:32,380
Sir,

194
00:13:32,650 --> 00:13:33,980
are you sick?

195
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:38,700
My...

196
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:40,510
My father is just like you.

197
00:13:43,140 --> 00:13:44,650
He’s in poor condition.

198
00:13:45,030 --> 00:13:46,300
A little cold

199
00:13:46,570 --> 00:13:47,880
could make him cough all day.

200
00:13:49,040 --> 00:13:50,330
I wonder

201
00:13:50,610 --> 00:13:51,980
if he’s taken

202
00:13:51,980 --> 00:13:53,420
good care of.

203
00:13:53,420 --> 00:13:54,300
I’m fine.

204
00:13:55,460 --> 00:13:56,890
I’ve had it for years.

205
00:14:04,760 --> 00:14:05,650
Sir,

206
00:14:06,320 --> 00:14:08,350
I took this from the post.

207
00:14:08,970 --> 00:14:10,200
It’s for those guards

208
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:11,110
and isn’t poisoned.

209
00:14:11,380 --> 00:14:12,180
They drug

210
00:14:12,180 --> 00:14:13,710
your food

211
00:14:13,710 --> 00:14:14,540
every day.

212
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:16,390
It’ll worsen your condition.

213
00:14:17,220 --> 00:14:19,160
You are already in poor health.

214
00:14:20,020 --> 00:14:21,840
Try to eat their food
as little as possible.

215
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:08,160
Do you know

216
00:15:08,160 --> 00:15:09,970
where your cousin is kept?

217
00:15:14,570 --> 00:15:15,530
No.

218
00:15:19,370 --> 00:15:21,400
And you still came regardless?

219
00:15:24,770 --> 00:15:27,870
Don’t you know who owns this place?

220
00:15:30,870 --> 00:15:31,650
I don’t.

221
00:15:34,270 --> 00:15:36,690
Have you heard of
the Four-guardian Mountain?

222
00:15:41,980 --> 00:15:44,220
What do you think

223
00:15:44,220 --> 00:15:46,620
an ignorant kid like you can do?

224
00:15:47,350 --> 00:15:49,730
Your family must be desperate.

225
00:15:50,550 --> 00:15:52,740
Who is he?

226
00:15:53,260 --> 00:15:54,660
He’s old

227
00:15:54,660 --> 00:15:56,150
and mean.

228
00:15:57,580 --> 00:15:59,020
Four-guardian Mountain

229
00:15:59,020 --> 00:16:00,930
was home to the evil

230
00:16:01,500 --> 00:16:03,090
headed by four leaders,

231
00:16:03,280 --> 00:16:05,650
claiming to be
the Four Guardians of the World.

232
00:16:05,800 --> 00:16:07,120
Truth is,

233
00:16:07,530 --> 00:16:10,250
they were a bunch of notorious villains,

234
00:16:13,050 --> 00:16:17,700
who threw the world into turmoil.

235
00:16:17,970 --> 00:16:20,860
Later, internal strife appeared

236
00:16:20,860 --> 00:16:22,280
when they came at each other

237
00:16:22,280 --> 00:16:24,540
and they disbanded.

238
00:16:25,640 --> 00:16:26,700
In the end,

239
00:16:27,660 --> 00:16:29,270
Phoenix and his followers

240
00:16:29,760 --> 00:16:31,840
settled down in Jingzhou

241
00:16:32,380 --> 00:16:34,390
and attached themselves to the Huo’s.

242
00:16:38,580 --> 00:16:40,050
Phoenix,

243
00:16:40,790 --> 00:16:42,680
Mu Xiaoqiao,

244
00:16:42,930 --> 00:16:45,140
once defeated

245
00:16:45,180 --> 00:16:47,140
three top masters of the Mount Tai Sect

246
00:16:47,140 --> 00:16:50,070
within half an hour

247
00:16:50,210 --> 00:16:53,960
and left safely under everyone’s watch.

248
00:16:55,730 --> 00:16:57,900
He sounds like a real piece of work.

249
00:16:58,930 --> 00:17:00,180
I must be careful.

250
00:17:01,310 --> 00:17:04,490
Why don’t I go get the antidotes first?

251
00:17:07,090 --> 00:17:08,890
You see what you got yourself into?

252
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:11,280
You won’t always be this lucky.

253
00:17:12,110 --> 00:17:13,070
Get lost.

254
00:17:15,450 --> 00:17:16,560
Thank you.

255
00:17:33,210 --> 00:17:34,730
The kitchen.

256
00:17:37,240 --> 00:17:40,130
The food must be poisoned

257
00:17:40,400 --> 00:17:43,360
in the kitchen

258
00:17:44,160 --> 00:17:46,190
where people come and go.

259
00:17:46,190 --> 00:17:47,610
Their own people might

260
00:17:48,350 --> 00:17:50,080
take the poisoned food by mistake.

261
00:17:50,930 --> 00:17:52,890
So they must have the antidotes.

262
00:17:54,020 --> 00:17:55,780
That chef

263
00:17:56,210 --> 00:17:57,990
may lead me to them.

264
00:18:29,940 --> 00:18:30,770
Lord,

265
00:18:31,160 --> 00:18:32,180
just now...

266
00:18:33,610 --> 00:18:34,810
That’s alright.

267
00:18:34,810 --> 00:18:36,240
It won’t

268
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:37,380
affect anything.

269
00:18:38,760 --> 00:18:41,170
Are you sure Phoenix is here?

270
00:18:41,510 --> 00:18:42,430
Yes.

271
00:18:42,980 --> 00:18:43,940
Good.

272
00:18:45,120 --> 00:18:47,080
My time is worth it.

273
00:18:48,370 --> 00:18:49,780
Stick to the plan.

274
00:18:49,990 --> 00:18:51,450
Once Tong Tianyang arrives,

275
00:18:51,450 --> 00:18:53,270
kill Mu Xiaoqiao first.

276
00:18:54,170 --> 00:18:56,230
Huo Liantao is nothing.

277
00:18:56,230 --> 00:18:57,090
Seize him

278
00:18:57,090 --> 00:18:59,180
and make him talk.

279
00:18:59,360 --> 00:19:00,160
Yes.

280
00:19:07,200 --> 00:19:08,140
Hold on.

281
00:19:19,650 --> 00:19:21,580
If you happen to

282
00:19:22,100 --> 00:19:23,380
see that girl,

283
00:19:23,770 --> 00:19:25,050
don’t kill her.

284
00:20:01,320 --> 00:20:02,700
Look what I’ve found!

285
00:20:04,750 --> 00:20:05,620
Didn’t I ask you to leave?

286
00:20:05,620 --> 00:20:06,850
Why are you back again?

287
00:20:07,390 --> 00:20:08,390
Open it.

288
00:20:16,370 --> 00:20:17,060
Come in.

289
00:20:18,350 --> 00:20:19,830
I don’t know what they are.

290
00:20:19,970 --> 00:20:20,830
Have a look.

291
00:20:25,430 --> 00:20:26,170
This is...

292
00:20:26,170 --> 00:20:27,040
the Heat-proof Pill.

293
00:20:32,200 --> 00:20:33,270
Kill-all Poison.

