00:20:38,550 --> 00:20:39,700
Styptic Powder.

295
00:20:40,650 --> 00:20:41,360
What’s this?

296
00:20:43,540 --> 00:20:44,420
Arsenic.

297
00:20:45,800 --> 00:20:47,160
