298
00:20:47,280 --> 00:20:48,090
What’s this?

299
00:20:49,730 --> 00:20:50,510
Aphrodi...

300
00:20:53,190 --> 00:20:55,430
Where did you get all these?

301
00:20:55,430 --> 00:20:56,600
