302
00:20:57,420 --> 00:20:58,380
What’s the last one?

303
00:20:58,730 --> 00:20:59,550
Uh...

304
00:21:00,220 --> 00:21:01,180
Well...

305
00:21:01,500 --> 00:21:02,240
That’s...

306
00:21:02,240 --> 00:21:03,730
