329
00:22:02,520 --> 00:22:03,590
Go against the crowd.

330
00:22:03,790 --> 00:22:05,540
Mu Xiaoqiao must be out battling them.

331
00:22:05,540 --> 00:22:06,970
Let’s go to his room.

332
00:22:08,930 --> 00:22:09,720
Let’s go.

333
00:22:13,780 --> 00:22:14,510
This way.

334
00:22:16,550 --> 00:22:18,200
Other than people of
the Fortress of the Forty-Eight,

335
00:22:18,560 --> 00:22:20,610
those of the Demons Manor sneaked in

336
00:22:20,610 --> 00:22:22,020
right under your nose, too.

337
00:22:22,770 --> 00:22:24,190
