338
00:22:25,540 --> 00:22:26,280
Who is it?

339
00:22:28,600 --> 00:22:29,480
Report!

340
00:22:29,480 --> 00:22:31,070
Phoenix asked me

341
00:22:31,070 --> 00:22:31,740
to fetch that thing in his room.

342
00:22:31,740 --> 00:22:32,710
Go ahead.

343
00:22:32,710 --> 00:22:33,440
Yes.

344
00:23:33,600 --> 00:23:34,460
Found it.

345
00:23:39,280 --> 00:23:40,180
Is this the antidote?

346
00:23:41,270 --> 00:23:43,110
How much should one take?

347
00:23:44,020 --> 00:23:44,840
Smelling it is enough.

348
00:23:44,840 --> 00:23:46,470
Too much of it is lethal.

349
00:23:49,310 --> 00:23:49,860
Let’s go!

350
00:23:54,360 --> 00:23:55,100
Hold on.

351
00:24:10,140 --> 00:24:11,110
What’s that?

352
00:24:13,850 --> 00:24:14,600
Oh, no!

353
00:24:15,420 --> 00:24:16,600
They’re going to blow up this place.

354
00:24:32,230 --> 00:24:33,540
