355
00:24:33,540 --> 00:24:35,090
Help! Let us out!

356
00:24:35,090 --> 00:24:35,920
Help!

357
00:24:36,680 --> 00:24:37,700
Help!

358
00:24:42,180 --> 00:24:43,400
This is the antidote.

359
00:24:43,400 --> 00:24:43,940
Thank you.

360
00:24:43,940 --> 00:24:44,960
Smell it.

361
00:24:50,600 --> 00:24:51,850
Come out.

362
00:24:54,670 --> 00:24:55,540
Hurry up and leave

363
00:24:55,540 --> 00:24:56,520
as soon as possible!

364
00:24:56,780 --> 00:24:57,740
Let’s go!

365
00:25:01,590 --> 00:25:02,260
