368
00:25:04,880 --> 00:25:05,900
I need to find them.

369
00:25:07,160 --> 00:25:07,980
Over there.

370
00:25:07,980 --> 00:25:08,800
This way.

371
00:25:15,200 --> 00:25:16,570
Go, go, go!

372
00:25:16,910 --> 00:25:18,350
Hurry!

373
00:25:19,590 --> 00:25:20,850
Let’s go!

374
00:25:21,990 --> 00:25:23,620
