-Let’s go.

375
00:25:23,620 --> 00:25:24,510
This way.

376
00:25:25,510 --> 00:25:26,930
Let’s go. Hurry up!

377
00:25:27,290 --> 00:25:27,880
Go!

378
00:25:27,880 --> 00:25:29,210
This way.

379
00:25:32,050 --> 00:25:32,940
Don’t worry.

380
00:25:32,940 --> 00:25:34,320
Judging by your cousin’s look,

381
00:25:34,320 --> 00:25:35,290
he still has many years to live.

382
00:25:36,110 --> 00:25:37,290
Even if he’s got the look,

383
00:25:37,410 --> 00:25:39,290
if Phoenix captures him,

384
00:25:39,290 --> 00:25:40,470
he’ll be...

385
00:25:47,720 --> 00:25:49,360
Huo Liantao!

386
00:25:52,680 --> 00:25:53,380
This way.

387
00:26:12,130 --> 00:26:13,590
-It’s him!
-It’s him!

388
00:26:18,820 --> 00:26:21,020
Huo Liantao, you bastard!

389
00:26:21,810 --> 00:26:23,020
Come out now!

390
00:26:28,990 --> 00:26:30,320
You know him?

391
00:26:31,190 --> 00:26:32,200
We met before.

392
00:26:33,790 --> 00:26:35,460
Demons may

393
00:26:35,900 --> 00:26:37,460
kill everyone

394
00:26:37,460 --> 00:26:38,410
in this place,

395
00:26:38,650 --> 00:26:40,990
including us.

396
00:26:41,620 --> 00:26:42,910
Just leave

397
00:26:42,910 --> 00:26:43,690
when you still can.

398
00:26:45,820 --> 00:26:46,560
This way.

399
00:26:56,790 --> 00:26:58,070
