404
00:27:04,390 --> 00:27:05,350
Sure.

405
00:27:05,350 --> 00:27:06,110
Give it to me.

406
00:27:08,720 --> 00:27:09,820
Seriously,

407
00:27:09,820 --> 00:27:11,340
