408
00:27:11,720 --> 00:27:13,200
Demons and Phoenix are all here.

409
00:27:13,200 --> 00:27:14,020
Do you want to die?

410
00:27:15,050 --> 00:27:16,110
I can’t abandon Li Sheng

411
00:27:16,110 --> 00:27:17,360
and Chenfei.

412
00:27:17,510 --> 00:27:18,920
If I leave

413
00:27:18,920 --> 00:27:19,810
without them,

414
00:27:20,400 --> 00:27:21,930
my mother will kill me.

415
00:27:22,300 --> 00:27:23,930
I’ve made a promise.

416
00:27:24,360 --> 00:27:25,480
Hey,

417
00:27:25,580 --> 00:27:27,480
is she really your mother?

418
00:27:27,700 --> 00:27:29,790
Does some promise weigh more
than your life?

419
00:27:29,790 --> 00:27:30,860
Yes!

420
00:27:38,260 --> 00:27:38,950
You’re right.

421
00:27:39,340 --> 00:27:40,780
A promise should be kept.

422
00:27:41,540 --> 00:27:43,000
No one’s life

423
00:27:43,060 --> 00:27:44,720
is more valuable than others’.

424
00:27:46,560 --> 00:27:47,390
Let’s go

425
00:27:47,870 --> 00:27:49,000
and get all those poor bastards

426
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:49,900
out of jail.

427
00:27:50,030 --> 00:27:51,630
The rest is up to heaven.

428
00:27:51,630 --> 00:27:52,970
And we won’t have any regrets.

429
00:27:55,740 --> 00:27:57,250
You’ve finally manned up for once.

430
00:28:00,610 --> 00:28:02,620
Who’d know a long-legged

431
00:28:02,620 --> 00:28:04,890
heartthrob like me

432
00:28:06,180 --> 00:28:07,590
would make friends with a dwarf?

433
00:28:07,960 --> 00:28:09,550
What are the odds?

434
00:28:11,250 --> 00:28:13,030
Why am I a dwarf?

435
00:28:15,020 --> 00:28:16,540
You aren’t even as tall

436
00:28:16,770 --> 00:28:18,060
as my legs, shorty.

437
00:28:29,620 --> 00:28:30,610
Master.

438
00:28:30,800 --> 00:28:31,890
Where’s Phoenix?

439
00:28:32,350 --> 00:28:33,650
There’s no sign of him.

440
00:28:33,650 --> 00:28:35,030
He’s here.

441
00:28:35,030 --> 00:28:36,180
Phoenix?

442
00:28:36,180 --> 00:28:38,310
No, Tong Tianyang of the Demons Manor.

443
00:28:38,310 --> 00:28:38,900
Who is he here for?

444
00:28:38,900 --> 00:28:40,010
For you.

445
00:28:40,960 --> 00:28:42,780
Our plan is doomed to fail.

446
00:28:43,720 --> 00:28:44,960
We need to find a shelter first.

447
00:28:44,960 --> 00:28:45,690
Let’s go!

448
00:28:52,720 --> 00:28:53,390
Come here.

449
00:28:53,390 --> 00:28:54,010
This is the antidote.

450
00:28:54,010 --> 00:28:54,690
Smell it.

451
00:28:54,690 --> 00:28:55,220
Thanks.

452
00:28:55,220 --> 00:28:56,270
The back door is at the end
on the left.

453
00:28:56,270 --> 00:28:56,860
Go.

454
00:28:56,860 --> 00:28:58,100
Let’s go!

455
00:28:58,100 --> 00:28:59,890
The back door is at the end on the left.

456
00:28:59,890 --> 00:29:00,510
Go.

457
00:29:02,440 --> 00:29:04,280
