458
00:29:05,240 --> 00:29:06,450
Smell the antidote.

459
00:29:07,980 --> 00:29:10,120
The back door is at the end
on the left. Go.

460
00:29:10,120 --> 00:29:10,590
Yes.

461
00:29:12,340 --> 00:29:13,060
Relax.

462
00:29:13,060 --> 00:29:14,910
I’ll protect your people.

463
00:29:15,850 --> 00:29:16,650
Thanks.

464
00:29:18,090 --> 00:29:19,590
Please wait.

465
00:29:20,290 --> 00:29:22,580
Thank you for saving my life.

466
00:29:22,700 --> 00:29:25,610
May I know your names?

467
00:29:26,510 --> 00:29:27,340
Two nobodies.

468
00:29:27,340 --> 00:29:28,310
No need to thank us.

469
00:29:28,520 --> 00:29:29,020
Fine.

470
00:29:29,020 --> 00:29:30,190
I’m in debt to you

471
00:29:30,190 --> 00:29:31,710
for saving me

472
00:29:31,710 --> 00:29:34,090
and I’ll pay you back in the future.

473
00:29:34,090 --> 00:29:34,840
Sir,

474
00:29:35,110 --> 00:29:36,570
didn’t you hear what I said?

475
00:29:37,340 --> 00:29:39,010
This place could explode anytime.

476
00:29:39,440 --> 00:29:40,900
I’m off.

477
00:29:45,560 --> 00:29:46,880
Huo Liantao,

478
00:29:48,240 --> 00:29:49,750
