00:30:50,980 --> 00:30:51,780
Nice!

498
00:30:51,780 --> 00:30:52,500
Fei,

499
00:30:52,500 --> 00:30:53,080
kill him!

500
00:30:53,080 --> 00:30:53,760
Zip it!

501
00:30:57,160 --> 00:30:58,200
Smell the antidote.

