512
00:31:41,550 --> 00:31:42,390
That’s right!

513
00:31:42,640 --> 00:31:43,860
She isn’t a master

514
00:31:43,860 --> 00:31:45,120
but she has what it takes

515
00:31:45,250 --> 00:31:46,610
to become one.

516
00:31:46,840 --> 00:31:47,900
