536
00:32:43,670 --> 00:32:44,490
Thanks.

537
00:32:47,950 --> 00:32:49,250
Miss Wu, smell the antidote.

538
00:32:57,300 --> 00:32:58,430
Don’t be afraid.

539
00:32:58,430 --> 00:33:00,190
Fei and I are of the same sect.

540
00:33:01,630 --> 00:33:03,850
They’re General Wu’s family,

541
00:33:04,630 --> 00:33:05,420
Miss Wu

542
00:33:05,630 --> 00:33:06,500
and Mr. Wu.

543
00:33:06,910 --> 00:33:07,930
Miss Wu,

544
00:33:08,620 --> 00:33:10,390
here’s dangerous. We should leave.

545
00:33:10,390 --> 00:33:11,690
Thank you, Fei.

546
00:33:11,950 --> 00:33:13,640
Others are kept over there.

547
00:33:13,640 --> 00:33:14,530
Give me a hand.

548
00:33:16,390 --> 00:33:17,410
Fei,

549
00:33:18,070 --> 00:33:19,090
aren’t you afraid?

550
00:33:21,860 --> 00:33:22,940
What’s there to be afraid?

551
00:33:23,230 --> 00:33:24,490
I’ll level this mountain

552
00:33:24,600 --> 00:33:25,960
