563
00:34:11,700 --> 00:34:12,730
A song

564
00:34:13,370 --> 00:34:14,730
telling how a beauty

565
00:34:14,910 --> 00:34:16,380
was abandoned by love before youth.

566
00:34:16,590 --> 00:34:18,440
Tears streamed down

567
00:34:18,820 --> 00:34:19,910
and smeared

568
00:34:20,240 --> 00:34:21,220
her makeup.

569
00:34:21,220 --> 00:34:22,030
I don’t understand a word.

570
00:34:23,940 --> 00:34:24,890
That’s Phoenix,

571
00:34:25,120 --> 00:34:25,910
