580
00:35:10,690 --> 00:35:13,030
only to make a living.

581
00:35:13,610 --> 00:35:17,160
I don’t think I owe you.

582
00:35:17,300 --> 00:35:19,160
If you need anything,

583
00:35:19,160 --> 00:35:20,790
feel free to tell me.

584
00:35:21,110 --> 00:35:22,590
Why go to

585
00:35:22,590 --> 00:35:24,050
